    <item>
      <title>苏丹军队从叛军民兵中夺回总统宫殿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/sudanese-army-enters-presidential-palace-reuters-reports-m8ieowt8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹的军队从叛军快速支撑军队准军事集团中撤回了首都的总统宫殿，该组织在一次残酷的内战中战斗了两年＆mdash;但是在城市继续战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/sudanese-army-enters-presidential-palace-reuters-reports-m8ieowt8</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其骚动提示里拉自2023年以来的最糟糕的每周务虚会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其里拉（Lira）在近两年内每周最陡峭的下降，随着紧急利率的增加未能阻止这种货币在越来越多的政治紧张局势中停止撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部说，特朗普内阁在委内瑞拉案中权衡了保密索赔。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/judge-calls-us-filing-woefully-insufficient-in-venezuela-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级司法部官员说，在法官对洛杉矶法院的披露爆炸后，他参与了“内阁级别的讨论”，以援引保密的主张，以掩盖有关驱逐涉嫌委内瑞拉帮派成员的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/judge-calls-us-filing-woefully-insufficient-in-venezuela-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 20:23:06 GMT</pubDate>
